# CODEOWNERS - Define code ownership and review requirements
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Note: Dependency files are excluded from CODEOWNERS to allow Renovate bot to automerge.
# This improves security by enabling automated dependency updates without manual intervention.

# ==============================================================================
# EXCLUSIONS FOR AUTOMATED DEPENDENCY MANAGEMENT
# ==============================================================================
# The following files are intentionally NOT owned to allow Renovate automerge:
# - package.json (npm dependencies)
# - package-lock.json (npm lockfile)
# - Gemfile.lock (Ruby dependencies)
# - renovate.json (Renovate configuration)
#
# Rationale: Automated dependency updates improve security posture by ensuring
# timely patching of vulnerabilities. Manual review adds latency without
# significant security benefit when CI gates are comprehensive.

# ==============================================================================
# CRITICAL SECURITY PATHS - Require explicit approval
# ==============================================================================

